gomodel:SYNGO_5394  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: S1PR4 was detected in synaptosomal biochemical fractions prepared from mouse cortex, with enrichment in the synaptosome-subfraction that enriches the active zone and its membrane (and possibly co-enriches proteins attached to the postsynaptic density membrane). S1PR4 was not detected in PSD fractions.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Synaptosomal fractionation was modified from Morato et al. [37]. Briefly, the mouse cortex was homogenized in 1 mL of isolation buffer ...\"\n\nantibody:\nRabbit anti-S1PR4, 1:1000 (WB)/1:250 (IFn)/1:100 (IFs), Novus (NBP2-24,500)" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2023-03-15" ;
